      <title>【实战】产品经理的逆袭：如何用 Claude Code 填平“不会写代码”的最后沟壑？</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%BB%8F%E7%90%86%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87claude-code-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3%E4%BB%8E%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E5%88%B0%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link>
